g.text: - Core UI/UX for tasks, calendar, notifications
- Primary entry point for internal logic
- Exposes REST endpoints for tasks, scheduling, notifications, user auth
- Weighted scoring of tasks (urgency, importance, due date)
- Classifies user queries into "Create Task", "Check Grades", etc.
- Identifies details: task name, date/time, course, etc.
- Stores tasks, events, user profiles, grade data, etc.
- Central data platform for advanced analytics
